Gabrielle Carmouche https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gabrielle_Carmouche 0 Gabrielle Carmouche (born May 22, 1978) is an American actress. She is best known for her role as Kateri Monroe on The Family Channel sitcom Big Brother Jake. She also had recurring roles in the sitcoms The Cosby Show in 1992 and In the House from 1996 to 1998 and made a guest appearance on Sister, Sister in 1996.
